  </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Harm Touch</span><hr size=1> I use it almost as soon as it pops everytime.<br>Unless I know that a particualliarly evil creature will attack me soon.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ufrenchhorn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FrenchHorn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 35<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/15/01 8:15:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Harm Touch</span><hr size=1> If I am about to die, I want to take something else down with me...<br><br><br><br>Lemeth,<br>Erudite Knight <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ucailgrimheart.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cail Grimheart</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/16/01 11:27:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Harm Touch</span><hr size=1> I only save it for life and death when I am in a risky environment, grouped or not.  The ability to suddenly do a few hundred points of damage in one strike can save the day.<br><br>If I am in a place where there is little or no risk, like hunting bears, or bandits, then I will use it on the next appropriate mob to cut down on fighting time. For example, I will HT the healers or spellcasters to minimize downtime.<br><br>If someone comes along trying to claim my kill, I will generally use my HT as well, if I think I may lose the kill.<br><br>I remember my first days on Firiona Vie in West Freeport, hunting rats and orcs with about 100 other people - I would fight, HT, and attack the guard to get my HT back.  It made for a lot of guaranteed kills, and secured me a rusty scythe very early on.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br> <p>Cail the Impatient<br>Knight of the League.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cerus>Cerus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/19/01 1:12:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Harm Touch</span><hr size=1> It depends alot.  If I am in a group, I tend to save it for a bad situation.  When I solo I tend to pull a little more aggresively when its up, so I end up using it shortly after it pops.  <br><br>Basically, I think Cail has the right of it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=morgrist>Morgrist</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 61<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/21/01 3:27:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Two reasons:</span><hr size=1> First,it's my way of stopping a fight quickly. Or at worst,making sure a fight turns at me rather than a silk-clad spellcaster that's getting shredded behind me because he chose the wrong kobold to mesmerize.<br> <br>Second,it's revenge. If I die,I'll hunt down the party responsible and give it to them,followed by my weapon through their chest-if I have a chance in Hate of doing them in.<br> <br>-Morgrist (League of Shadows)<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uroninsenshi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RoninSenshi</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Kanji.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Senshi No Adakia</span><br>  Posts: 113<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/21/01 5:58:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Kanji.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Two reasons:</span><hr size=1> When Killing Paladins, when I am going to die.<br><br>OR when fighting an opponet that pisses me off.<br><br> <p><IMG SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou.gif">Shintou Shinai</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubraellarth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Braellarth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/22/01 9:00:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> i use it when...</span><hr size=1> If i am solo, i save it. If i am in a group that is risky, i save it. If i am in a nice group i dont have to be scared for my life every second or two, i use it as soon as fell its nagging pain in my sides.<br><br>I believe my Harm touch is deity given, Innoruuk flows in by blood, i restrain the hate until it is a powerfull instrument then purge it from my body, channeling it through my hands and into my target.<br>The loss of innoruuk is a relief and burden, the feeling is pure hatred and twisted pain.. yet at the same time addictive. Without it i morn the loss until again i feel it bursting to be released!<br><br>All praise Innoruuk our lord and creator. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umadrain.showPublicProfile?language=EN>madrain</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 26<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/25/01 8:16:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: i use it when...</span><hr size=1> All of my times have already been said.  I like to save it...I won't waste it on blue mobs unless I'm near death.  I sometimes use it when I'm pissed, like if I miss 5 times in a row.  I use it often to keep a kill on my side of the exp rather than someone else who jumps in.<br><br>Since I've only been in 2 groups now, both with the same barbarian, I solo alot.  So I find myself taking on a large number of whites whenever possible, and the occasional yellow if I have my Harm Touch handy.  Normally I can fight them to around halfway and I have a bubble or possibly two, then use Harm Touch.  With luck they turn and run and I can finish them off, but some yellows are persistent...such as the kobold I fought today who had maybe 5 hp left when he murdered me. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukentassolgaard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kentas Solgaard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 62<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/26/01 10:31:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.personal.psu.edu/students/b/t/btk120/MOKONA.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Harm Touch</span><hr size=1> I use it for three reasons:<br><br>1.  I need an advantage, and quick.<br><br>2.  Someone else is trying to get credit for my work.<br><br>3.  To save myself the trouble of killing its friends should it run for them.  (Fear can translate into pain.)<br><br> <p>--Antoin Radib<br>EverQuest: Firiona Vie Server<br>"I always give alcohol to dwarves.  Marinades 'em from the inside out."</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uzenblend.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ZenBlend</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/30/02 3:13:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Harm Touch</span><hr size=1> I save it and use it when:<br><br>1.) I'm fighting a white/yellow solo and get an add.<br><br>2.) Running away from that damn red who jumped me. I'm probably gunna die anyway. This way he gets to feel a little pain as well. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ukataklystikmacail.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KataklystikMacail</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Morally Challanged</span><br>  Posts: 82<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/16/02 2:44:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Harm Touch</span><hr size=1> Harm touch<br><br> - When fighting tougher-than-average mobs (ravashing Drols, Cappy, giants with allota hps)<br> -  Emergency Taunt(the mobs sure love you after you smack 500+ damage on them in one hit)<br> - When dying<br> - Supprise casters in duels <br> - To get caster mobs down fast<br> <br>Generally, i try to use HT as soon as possible. But i never waste it on 20onadozen-mobs, unless the casters/healers are oom or i need some Hate fast.<br><br>I always use my HT as fast as possible when soloing, reduces mana usage and downtime by loads. <p><hr><h4><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=68002"><b>Macail Deghoulish</b></h4></a></p><p><b>Erudite</b> SK 49th Fear<br><a href="http://www.geocities.com/dragansouls"><i>Dragan Souls</i></a><br>Tholuxe Paells</p><h6><i>"Hell yea my STR sucks, but have you seen many other male SKs with a dress??"</i></h6></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utwotribes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Twotribes</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Board Troll</span><br>  Posts: 284<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/17/02 10:07:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=12>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Harm Touch</span><hr size=1> Grong uses his when he is dieing (if he remembers).<br><br>He also uses it to finish a mob when a second or more shows up.<br><br>In a group he tends to hold it, in case it is needed to help the weaklings he is grouped with.<br><br>Grong Gnorg is currently a 27th LEVEL Ogre Shadowknight on Karana. As a follower of Rallos Zek he believes the strong right arm is the way to go. But he understands his spells and Harm Touch are gifts (though not always useful, Rallos does prefer the blood of a good fight) from somewhere.<br><br>As a Knight of Rallos he does consider the safety of the lesser races and weaklings he associates with. He is after all a Knight.<br><br>Now my other Shadowknights are a Tier'Dal (10th level) and an Erudite (6th lvl, and never been to painell, made before then) neither is as experienced with the Harm Touch. Both tend to use it for self only.<br><br>I tend to horde the Touch, it takes 90 real minutes (one Norrathian Day) to get it back and you never know when you might need it again.<br><br>I only use it on Red mobs if my spells have worked on them or I am dieing. Since Death resets it and not using it was a waste after all. Grong wont use it in a group on a red unless his spells have landed. It is a waste to channel the power and have nothing happen. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showPrevMessage?topicID=31.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showNextMessage?topicID=31.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=12><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.threadControl?topicID=31.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http: